# 📚 Books Deal — Secondhand Book Marketplace for Nepal

> A full-stack web application where users can buy and sell secondhand books — built for Nepal, inspired by platforms like OLX.

🌐 **Live:** [booksdeal.com.np](https://book-store-five-xi-70.vercel.app) &nbsp;|&nbsp; 📦 **Backend:** [Render](https://book-store-1-zx4o.onrender.com)

---

## Overview

Books Deal is a secondhand book marketplace built for Nepali users. The same account can act as both a buyer and a seller — list your old books, browse others, add to cart, and pay securely via eSewa.

---

## Features

### 👤 Authentication
- Register and login with JWT stored in httpOnly cookies
- Email verification via OTP before login is allowed
- 30-day session with secure cookie management

### 📖 Books
- List books for sale with title, price, condition, and images
- Browse and search available books
- Edit or delete your own listings
- Books automatically marked as **Sold** after successful purchase

### 🛒 Cart & Checkout
- Add multiple books to cart
- Multi-book checkout in a single transaction
- Delivery address selection at checkout

### 💳 Payment (eSewa v2)
- Integrated eSewa v2 payment gateway
- HMAC-SHA256 signature generation and verification
- Base64-encoded callback handling
- Secondary status API confirmation for payment integrity
- Automatic order creation only after successful payment

### 📦 Orders
- View purchase history as a buyer
- View sales history as a seller
- Delivery address stored per order

### 👤 Profile
- View and edit profile details
- Switch between buyer and seller mode

