## Key Architecture Decisions

- **Same-origin cookies** — Vercel proxy rewrites `/api/*` to Render backend, so cookies work across all browsers including Brave and Safari
- **Orders after payment** — Orders are only created after eSewa confirms successful payment, never before
- **Multi-book transactions** — `book_ids` stored as a JSON array in the Transaction model to support cart purchases
- **Delivery address** — Stored as direct columns in Order (not FK) to avoid conflicts if address is deleted
- **UUID primary keys** — Used throughout all models
- **Email verification** — OTP-based, login blocked until verified

